title: 21. Real Talk: The Gift Of The Quarantine
itunes:title: 21. Real Talk: The Gift Of The Quarantine
description: What are you doing with your time during this quarantine? There was an article posted by Forbes Magazine, basically shaming those who are using the extra time to their advantage and progressing themselves, compared to those who are drinking more, smoking weed, and watching porn. In today's episode, I talk about how you can use this time to your advantage and come out dominating.
